Description:
	ISO/IEC 2022 based 7-bit encoding for Japanese.
	
	This coding system is defined by Junet no tebiki,
	RFC 1468, JIS X 0208:1997 Appendix 2 and bis1468
	(an expired Internet Draft).
}

